  <brief_title>Chondroitin Sulphate Treatment Efficacy in Rhizarthrosis.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Chondroitin Sulphate Treatment Efficacy in Rhizarthrosis. Measurement With Sensory and Quantitive Functional Tests and Concordance Analysis With Subjective Scales of Pain.</official_title>
