  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients who present rhizarthrosis diagnostic will be randomized to be treated with
      chondroitin sulfate or placebo during 24 weeks to study the effect of the treatment with
      objective and subjective indicators of pain and sensibility.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
